data.description: Wonderfully upgraded 2 bed+den/2.5 bath home with mountain and golf course views. Beautiful Great room and upgraded kitchen with pull out shelving, solid surface counters. Plantation shutters throughout the home and LVP flooring throughout (no carpet). All fixtures, lights, toilets updated. Owned solar system, whole home water filtration system (not salt), low maintenance landscaping, three citrus trees. Could also be great seasonal or long-term rental in this beautiful, popular golf community with so many amenities!
